  "texts": [
    "This setup reduces the load on the LLM to learn vision-language alignment, mitigating the risk of the catastrophic forgetting problem.",
    "General Vision-Language Instruction TuningFollowing the pretraining phases, as in Dai et al [23], Q-Former undergoes a vision-language instruction tuning process.",
    "Here, the LLM integrates visual encodings from Q-Former with additional instruction text tokens.",
    "The instruction interacts with the query embeddings through the Q-Former's self-attention layers.",
    "This interaction aids in extracting relevant image features, which are further provided to optimize the LLM for following instructions."
  ],
